sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant UI as Main Window (App.tsx)
  participant Perm as macOS Permission Plugin
  participant Cmd as Tauri Commands (invoke)
  participant Runtime as RuntimeController
  participant Hotkeys as FnShortcutManager
  participant Bus as Event Bus (steno://*)

  User->>UI: Launch app
  UI->>UI: Register listeners (state/transcription/interim/error/models)
  UI->>Perm: Check accessibility + microphone + input monitoring

  alt Any required permission missing
    UI->>UI: Show permission remediation screen
  else Permissions satisfied
    UI->>Cmd: initialize_runtime()
    Cmd->>Runtime: ensure_settings_loaded()
    Runtime->>Runtime: normalize + persist settings
    Runtime->>Hotkeys: initialize shortcuts with timeout
    Runtime->>Bus: emit steno://state-changed
    Runtime->>Bus: emit steno://model-download-state-changed
    Bus-->>UI: deliver initial snapshots
    UI->>UI: render Overview/Settings screens
  end
